Shirye-shiryen Sainsbury na turawa zuwa kasuwar kyakkyawa ta Burtaniya
Sainsbury's na cinyewa Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams tare da shagunan kayan kwalliya masu kyau da ke da kwararrun ma'aikata.
A wani bangare na gagarumin turawa zuwa kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya ta fam biliyan 2.8, wacce ke ci gaba da bunkasa yayin da tallace-tallace na kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke raguwa, za a gwada manyan hanyoyin kayan kwalliyar a shaguna 11 a duk fadin kasar kuma za a kai su wasu shaguna a shekara mai zuwa idan ta samu nasara.
Wannan zuba jari a cikin kyau ya zo ne yayin da manyan kantuna ke neman hanyoyin da za su yi amfani da sararin ɗakunan da aka yi amfani da su don talabijin, microwaves da kayan gida.
Sainsbury's ta ce za ta ninka girman kayan kwalliyarta zuwa samfurori 3,000, gami da alamomi kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw a karon farko.
Hakanan za a sami ƙarin sarari daga L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees tare da wuraren da aka yi wa alama kamar waɗanda aka samo a shaguna kamar Boots.
Har ila yau, babban kanti yana sake ƙaddamar da kayan kwalliyar Boutique don yawancin kayayyakin su kasance masu cin ganyayyaki - wani abu da matasa masu sayayya ke buƙata.
Bugu da kari, mai sayar da turare Fragrance Shop zai gwada cinikin a shaguna biyu na Sainsbury, na farko daga cikinsu ya bude a Croydon, kudancin Landan, a makon da ya gabata yayin da na biyu zai bude a Selly Oak, Birmingham, a karshen wannan shekarar.
Kasuwancin kan layi da sauyawa zuwa siyan ƙananan abinci a kowace rana a shagunan abinci na gida yana nufin manyan kantuna suna buƙatar yin ƙarin don shawo kan mutane su ziyarci.
Mike Coupe, babban daraktan Sainsbury's, ya ce wuraren za su zama kamar manyan kantuna yayin da sarkar manyan kantuna ke kokarin yin gwagwarmaya da masu rage farashin Aldi da Lidl tare da karin ayyuka da kayan abinci.
Sainsbury's ta sanya kantunan Argos a daruruwan shaguna kuma ta kuma gabatar da wasu wuraren zama tun lokacin da ta sayi sarƙoƙin biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, wanda ta ce ya ƙarfafa tallace-tallace na kayan abinci kuma ya sa sayayya ya fi riba.
Ƙoƙarin da aka yi a baya na sake gyara sashen gyaran kayan ado da kuma kantin magani ya ƙare a rashin nasara.
Sainsbury's ya gwada haɗin gwiwa tare da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma haɗin gwiwa ya ƙare bayan rikici game da yadda za a raba kudaden shiga daga kantin magani a cikin manyan kantunansa.
Sabuwar dabarar ta zo ne bayan da Sainsbury ta sayar da kasuwancin kantin magani 281 ga Celesio, mai mallakar sarkar kantin magani ta Lloyds, don £ 125m, shekaru uku da suka gabata.
Ya ce Lloyds zai taka rawa a cikin shirin, ta hanyar ƙara fadada kewayon alamun kayan kwalliyar fata na alatu ciki har da La Roche-Posay da Vichy a cikin shaguna huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury's, ya ce: "Mun canja siffar da kuma yanayin wuraren da muke sayar da kayan ado don mu kyautata yanayin da abokan cinikinmu suke ciki.
Mun kuma zuba jari a cikin abokan aiki da aka horar da su musamman waɗanda za su kasance a wurin don ba da shawara.
An tsara samfuranmu don dacewa da kowane buƙata kuma yanayin da ke jan hankali da wurare masu dacewa suna nufin yanzu mun zama kyakkyawan kyakkyawan makoma wanda ke ƙalubalanci tsohuwar hanyar cin kasuwa. "
Peter Jones 'mai fushi' bayan Holly Willoughby ya janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Dragon Den Peter Jones ya bar 'haushi' bayan mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ya janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 tare da kasuwancinsa na rayuwa don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarta tare da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don kayan gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin su da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop alama.
Mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, mai shekara 37, ta dauki Instagram don sanar da cewa ta tafi.
Holly Willoughby ta bar tauraron 'Dragons' Den Peter Jones cikin fushi ta hanyar janyewa daga kasuwancin kasuwancin rayuwarsu mai riba a minti na ƙarshe - don mai da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarta tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyi sun ce Jones ya "yi fushi" lokacin da yarinyar zinariya ta TV ta yarda a yayin wani taro mai tsauri a ranar Talata a hedkwatar daular kasuwancinsa a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin yarjejeniyoyinta - masu darajar £ 1.5 miliyan - na nufin ba ta da isasshen lokaci don sadaukar da kayan ado da kayan haɗi na gida Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop alama kuma an ba da shawarar ninka dukiyar Willoughby da aka kiyasta £ 11 miliyan.
Yayin da Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ta dauki Instagram don sanar da cewa tana barin Truly, Jones ya tashi daga Burtaniya don zuwa daya daga cikin gidajen hutunsa.
Wani majiya ya ce: "Gaskiya ita ce ta fi muhimmanci ga Holly.
Wannan zai kasance makomar ta ta dogon lokaci wanda zai gan ta ta cikin shekaru biyu masu zuwa.
Shawarwarin da ta yanke na janyewa ya ba kowa mamaki.
Babu wanda ya yarda da abin da ke faruwa a ranar Talata, yana kusa da kaddamarwa.
Akwai wani sito cike da kaya a hedkwatar Marlow da suke shirye su sayar. "
Masana sun yi imanin cewa barin mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, wanda ke cikin taurari masu daraja a Burtaniya, na iya kashe kamfanin miliyoyin saboda saka hannun jari mai yawa a cikin kayayyaki daga matashin kai da kyandirori zuwa tufafi da kayan gida, da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkiri ga ƙaddamar da shi.
Kuma hakan zai iya nufin ƙarshen abokantaka mai tsawo.
Mahaifiyar yara uku Willoughby da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance kusa da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp har tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a cikin 2016 kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga matsayin shugaban a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata suna hutu tare kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin dari a kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby zai zama jakadan alama don M & S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da ITV Na kasance Mai Shahara.
Wata majiya da ke kusa da Jones ta ce a daren jiya "Ba za mu yi tsokaci kan harkokin kasuwancinsa ba".
