John Goldsmith, shugaban Ƙungiyar Cromwell, ya ce: "A cikin muhawara da ake yi yanzu game da cire mutummutumai, ba za a iya guje wa cewa mutum na Oliver Cromwell a waje da Fadar Westminster zai zama makasudi ba.
Cromwell bai ba da umurni ko kuma ya aiwatar da wannan mugun aikin ba.
Wataƙila za a yi hadaya da Cromwell da ba daidai ba saboda ayyukan kakansa Thomas a ƙarni na baya.
Sir William Hamo Thorneycroft mai ban mamaki na Cromwell hujja ce ta ra'ayi na karni na 19 kuma wani ɓangare na tarihin wani adadi wanda mutane da yawa sun gaskata har yanzu ya cancanci bikin.
Mista Goldsmith ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Telegraph: "Mutane da yawa suna ganin Cromwell, wataƙila a ƙarshen ƙarni na 19 fiye da yadda yake a yau, a matsayin mai kare majalisa daga matsin lamba daga waje, a cikin shari'arsa, ba shakka, mulkin mallaka.
