Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 sun kalli shaidar ranar Alhamis ta wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i wanda ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da watsa shirye-shiryen da ke katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don juyawa na ƙarshe na ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da binciken mako guda game da tuhumar.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ta tabbata da kashi 100 cikin 100 cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata taɓo cikin maye kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta a wata liyafar makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar sha'awar, ya ce yana da 100% tabbata cewa bai faru ba.
Da alama fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a sun kalli shi.
Kamfanin yana kirga matsakaicin masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai ba nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin da suka nuna shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen auna mutanen da ke kallon a ofisoshi.
Don sanya wannan a cikin hangen nesa, wannan girman masu sauraro ne mai kama da na wasan kwallon kafa na wasan kwaikwayo ko kuma kyautar Academy.
Tashar Fox News, wacce masu gabatar da ra'ayi suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ta jagoranci dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a yayin sauraron ranar, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3.1, NBC tana da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC tana da miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN tana da miliyan 2.52, Nielsen ya ce.
Har ila, mutane sun ci gaba da son wannan jawabin.
Flake shi ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin 'yan Republican masu matsakaici ya fitar da wata sanarwa cewa zai kada kuri'a a madadin Kavanaugh, an kama shi a kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a ana ihu da masu zanga-zangar yayin da yake kokarin hawa lif zuwa sauraron Kwamitin Shari'a.
Ya tsaya da idanunsa a ƙasa na tsawon minti da dama yayin da aka yi masa tsawa, wanda aka watsa kai tsaye a talabijin a CNN.
Wata mata ta ce: "Ina tsaye a gabanka.
"Kuna ganin yana gaya wa kasar gaskiya?
An gaya masa, "kuna da iko lokacin da mata da yawa ba su da iko. ""
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da wata sanarwa kuma ya ce, kafin a rufe lif din, zai kara da cewa a zaman kwamitin.
Tashoshin talabijin da na talabijin duk suna watsa shirye-shiryen ne a kai tsaye bayan wasu sa'o'i, lokacin da Kwamitin Shari'a zai kada kuri'a don ciyar da takarar Kavanaugh zuwa majalisar dattijai don jefa kuri'a.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai tare da fahimtar cewa FBI za ta bincika zargin da ake yi wa ɗan takarar a mako mai zuwa, wanda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya tabbata a wani bangare ta hanyar tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na Democrat.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai bayan haka, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Zaɓin Flake yana da iko, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da bincike ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
