Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia, kuma ana ganin adadin mutanen da suka mutu yana ƙaruwa
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu, da yawa sun tafi yayin da manyan raƙuman ruwa suka afku a rairayin bakin teku, lokacin da wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afku a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, in ji hukumomi a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin a bakin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu ranar Juma'a lokacin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi mita shida suka buge bakin teku da yamma, suna shafe mutane da yawa zuwa mutuwarsu kuma suna lalata duk abin da ke cikin hanyarsu.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
"Lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta tashi jiya, mutane har yanzu suna yin ayyukansu a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu nan da nan ba kuma sun zama waɗanda aka kashe", in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar rage bala'in Indonesiya BNPB a wani taron da aka yi a Jakarta.
"Tsunami din bai zo da kansa ba, ya ja motoci, katako, gidaje, ya buge komai a ƙasa", in ji Nugroho, yana mai cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya a cikin teku mai sauri da sauri na kilomita 800 a kowace awa kafin ya buga gabar teku.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun hau bishiyoyi don tserewa tsunami kuma sun tsira.
An kwashe mutane kusan 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a Palu.
Hotunan sama da hukumar bala'in ta fitar sun nuna gine-gine da shaguna da yawa da aka lalata, gadoji da suka karye kuma suka rushe da masallaci da ke kewaye da ruwa.
An ci gaba da girgizar ƙasa a garin da ke bakin teku a ranar Asabar.
An ji girgizar ƙasa a yankin da ke da mutane miliyan 2.4.
Hukumar tantancewa da amfani da fasaha ta Indonesia (BPPT) ta ce a cikin wata sanarwa makamashin da girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta saki ranar Juma'a ya ninka karfin bam din atomatik da aka jefa a Hiroshima a yakin duniya na biyu sau 200.
An ce yanayin birnin, wanda ke ƙarshen wani doguwar, ƙanƙanin bakin teku, zai iya ƙara girman tsunami, in ji shi.
Nugroho ya bayyana lalacewar a matsayin "mai yawa" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun rushe.
An gano gawarwakin wasu wadanda aka kashe a karkashin tarwatsewar gine-ginen da suka rushe, in ji shi, ya kara da cewa mutane 540 sun ji rauni kuma 29 sun bace.
Nugroho ya ce asarar rayuka da lalacewar na iya zama mafi girma a gabar tekun kilomita 300 (190 miles) arewacin Palu, wani yanki da ake kira Donggala, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar.
Sadarwa "ta kasance cikakke ba tare da wani bayani ba" daga Donggala, in ji Nugroho.
Akwai mutane sama da 300,000 da ke zaune a can, "in ji Red Cross a cikin wata sanarwa, ta kara da cewa ma'aikatanta da masu sa kai suna kan hanyarsu zuwa yankunan da abin ya shafa.
