LeBron zai fara wasan Lakers ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Da kyar aka gama jiran magoya baya da ke neman ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa na ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma har yanzu ba a san yawan mintuna da zai buga ba.
"Zai kasance fiye da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48, "in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa cewa mai yiwuwa James zai taka minti kadan.
