Lokacin Taron Trump na Yammacin Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara gangamin yakin neman zabe a wannan karon a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na Trump na biyar da aka tsara a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da tsayar da kuri'ar tabbatarwa don zabarsa don cike gurbin Kotun Koli, Trump yana da nufin gina goyon baya ga za ~ en tsakiyar wa'adi masu zuwa tunda 'yan Republican suna cikin haɗarin rasa ikon Majalisa lokacin da aka jefa kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana yau da dare kuma ta yaya za ku kalli kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump na Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma ET yau da dare, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye akan YouTube.
Trump na iya jawabi a wannan makon a zaman sauraron wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai matukar damuwa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i tare da zaben tabbatar da Majalisar Dattawa da ake tsammani a cikin mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan gangamin taron shi ne taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
Don haka, kamfen din Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan gangamin guda biyar a mako mai zuwa suna da nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai, " a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar mahimmanci ga ajandar sa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin kamfen", in ji mai magana da yawun kamfen na Trump wanda ya ƙi bayyana sunansa ga Reuters.
An shirya shi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare na iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma su jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne dai Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don kokarin ba shi ci gaba a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta nuna ƙarfin hali don yin gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan rayuwa zuwa ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman uku na gefe guda, wasan hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma zai iya zama abin da wannan gasar Ryder Cup ke bukata.
Tsuntsu mai juyawa na motsi shine cikakkiyar manufar wasanni amma wanda 'yan wasan suka gaskanta da gaske, kuma ba fiye da irin wannan ba.
To ina za su ce motsin yana yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka muna ɗaukar wannan a matsayin ɗan ƙaramin motsi ina tsammanin", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake tafiya don ranar.
Turai tana da fa'ida, ba shakka, maki hudu a gaba da kuma karin goma sha biyu a wasa.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin suna da iska a cikin jirgin ruwa kuma suna da yawa don karfafawa, ba ma kadan daga cikin yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare a duk rana kuma kowannensu yana da maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai kisa daga tee zuwa kore kuma yana jagoranci ta hanyar misali.
Wadannan kururuwan murna na murna sun kara karfi yayin da zagaye ya ci gaba, yana nutsewa a cikin wani muhimmin abu don daukar wasan hudu a duk lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu bayan biyu.
An yi ma sa irin wannan ihu a lokacin da ya jefa kwallo da ya lashe wasan a raga ta 15. Wannan ya nuna cewa ya yi imanin cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta fita daga wannan.
"A gaskiya sai ka yi zurfin bincike kuma ka damu da abin da kake so", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne duk wanda kowane daga cikin 'yan wasan da aka bari a yanzu.
Ramin 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin da ba za a iya jayayya da shi ba na gasar Ryder.
