Turai ta ci gaba da kaiwa 10-6 a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder
Turai za ta samu ci gaba a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan fitowa daga wasannin hudu da hudu na ranar Asabar tare da 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci cajin tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai fama don ɗaukar ƙididdigar su har zuwa yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke neman rike kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara a kan kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka da ta gaza a wasan safiya, inda ta lashe jerin 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya cinye rashi ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas daga wasannin 12 na ranar Lahadi domin rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine dan wasa na farko na Turai da ya lashe maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka lakafta "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki sune kawai biyu biyu da suka lashe maki hudu daga wasannin farko hudu a tarihin gasar Ryder.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin hudu-balls sai suka yi kyau sosai don su doke Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau ta hanyar 5 & 4.
Woods, wanda ya ja kansa ta hanyar wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu lokuta na haske amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasannin 29 a cikin hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, ya huta don wasannin safiya, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu zuwa 2 & 1 da aka doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - na ɗaya da na uku a duniya.
Turai ba ta da komai yadda ta so ko da yake a rana mai kyau, mai iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa ma'auni ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2 & 1 akan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin hudu kuma sun dawo daga baya don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4 & 3 a cikin huɗu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup ta samu tawagar da ta dawo daga rashin maki hudu a cikin guda, ko da yake a matsayin masu riƙe da Furyk, ƙungiyar ta kawai ta bukaci ta riƙe kyautar.
Amma bayan sun kasance na biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, harin na ranar Lahadi yana kama da cewa ba za su iya ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce 'babu yadda za'ayi' ta kwance makamai ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumi yana kara tsananta rashin amincewar da kasar ke yi wa Amurka kuma babu yadda kasar za ta yi ta daina makaman nukiliyarta a wani bangare a irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar ta duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na kyautatawa" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, rushe wurin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin ba za a yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani amsa daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da wani amincewa a Amurka ba za a sami amincewa a cikin tsaron kasa ba kuma a irin wannan yanayi babu yadda za mu yi da kanmu a cikin makamai".
Yayin da Ri ya sake maimaita korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta saba da shi game da juriyar Washington ga tsarin "mataki-mataki" na kawar da makaman nukiliya wanda za a ba wa Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da ta ɗauki matakai a hankali, bayaninsa ya bayyana mai mahimmanci a cikin cewa bai ƙi yarda da haramta makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "kawar da makaman nukiliya daga yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara barin makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan "rashin nukiliya-farko" kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinsu ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma da adawa da "bayyanar karshen yaki", "in ji Ri.
"Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya sa mu durƙusa a gwiwoyi mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da takunkumi yana ƙara sa mu ƙara rashin amincewa da juna".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya nuna a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka ministan ya nuna tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: "Idan bangaren wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, kawar da makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ba zai zo ga irin wannan matsalar ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na bara, lokacin da ya fadawa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa kai hari ga Amurka da makaman rokokin Koriya ta Arewa ba makawa ne bayan "Mista Shugaba Mugun" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makami mai linzami" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa wajen daukar matakan kwance makamai, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi hakan, yana cewa "Idan zai dauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar - ba shi da mahimmanci".
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kamata ta ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Dole ne a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro da ƙarfi kuma ba tare da kasawa ba har sai mun cimma cikakken, ƙarshe, tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Majalisar Tsaro ta kara sanya takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun daga shekarar 2006 a kokarin dakile kudaden da ake baiwa shirin nukiliya da makaman rokoki na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma ya ce daga baya zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, sai dai Koriya ta Arewa a cikin sa'o'i kadan ta yi masa kashedi saboda yin "bukatun da suka yi kama da na 'yan daba".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a wani taro da Moon a wannan watan da za ta rushe wani wurin kera makamai masu linzami da kuma wani makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema sune garantin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matsawa zuwa daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna yin darasi a samun isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa dukkan dalibanta su kara bacci a kokarin yaki da al'adar maza da ke karuwa na karatu ta hanyar shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a makarantar likitancin Harvard kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da na mata, ya tsara wannan kwas, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko irin sa a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don fara karatun bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci akan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshen taron, wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce: 'Me ya sa yanzu ne aka gaya mini wannan, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?'
Ta ce babu wanda ya taba gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci - wanda ya ba ni mamaki,' in ji shi ga The Telegraph.
Wannan kwas din, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimman abubuwan da suka shafi yadda kyawawan halaye na bacci ke taimakawa aikin ilimi da wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu gaba daya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin hauka a makarantar likitancin Harvard kuma darektan zartarwa na ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun bayan gano cewa dalibai suna fama da matsalar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na tsawon awa daya ya kunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kan kofunan kofi, labule, masu motsa jiki da littattafai don a gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da yadda rashin bacci ke shafar aikin motsa jiki, da kuma mahimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, ana gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, bakin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumakan hulɗa, sannan yana ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullun.
'Mun san ba zai canza halin dalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da hakkin sanin hakan - kamar yadda ku ma kuke da hakkin sanin illolin shan taba sigari a kan lafiyarku,' in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar alfahari da 'yin aiki na dare' har yanzu tana wanzu, in ji shi, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma karuwar matsin lamba a kan dalibai ya nuna rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Tabbatar da samun isasshen barci, mai inganci, ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' na ɗalibi don yaƙar damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi - har ma don kauce wa samun nauyi, kamar yadda rashin barci ya sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa su ci gaba da yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan shekara 19 daga California da ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da ilimin halittu, ya taimaki Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin, bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekarar da ta shige a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya bude masa idanu kuma ya karfafa masa gwiwa ya turawa makarantar gaba daya.
Mataki na gaba, ya yi fatan, shi ne a nemi dukkan daliban da ke karatun digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan shirin karatun kafin su shiga makarantar da ke gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa don lokacin da za su kwanta, da kuma lokacin da za su farka, kuma su san illolin 'hasken shuɗi' da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya sa yanayin rayuwarka ya lalace, yana haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Menga ta ci kwallo ta kashe mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sake fuskantar wani mummunan yanayi yayin da bugun Dolly Menga ya sa Steven Gerrard ya ci 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox na neman cin nasarar farko a kan hanya tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da aka yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi rashin nasara ta biyu ga Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin koci don barin tawagarsa maki takwas daga jagorancin Ladbrokes Hearts.
Menga ya buga minti bakwai kafin hutun rabin lokaci kuma Rangers ba su da isharar da ta dace.
Yayin da Rangers yanzu suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku kuma kawai a bayan Hibernian a bambancin burin.
Kuma za a iya samun matsala a cikin kantin sayar da kaya ga Rangers bayan da aka kula da Calum Spence don rauni a kai bayan an jefa wani abu daga ƙarshen.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a ƙungiyar da ta wuce Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na Betfred Cup.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya tafi tare da wannan Livi 11 wanda ya dauki maki daga Zuciya a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda tufafinsa mai kyau ya shafe abokan adawarsu a kowane lokaci.
Rangers na iya mamaye mallakar kwallon amma Livingston ya yi fiye da yadda suke da shi.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo a minti biyu da suka wuce lokacin da Menga ya fara jefa Scott Pittman a raga ta Allan McGregor amma dan wasan tsakiya ya kori babbar damarsa.
Wani bugun kirji mai zurfi na Keaghan Jacobs ya sami kyaftin Craig Halkett amma abokin aikinsa na karewa Alan Lithgow kawai zai iya yin amfani da shi a baya.
Rangers sun dauki iko amma akwai fatan da yawa game da wasan su a kashi na uku na karshe.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji ya kamata a hukunta shi a lokacin da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless amma alkalin wasa Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da roko na dan kasar Colombia.
Rangers sun samu nasarar buga kwallo biyu a raga a farkon rabin wasan amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox Liam Kelly bai damu da bugun kai na Lassana Coulibaly da kuma bugun Ovie Ejaria ba.
Duk da cewa Livi ya fara wasa a minti na 34 ba zai yi wasa ba, amma babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan saboda cin hanci da rashawa.
Har yanzu Rangers sun kasa magance wani babban Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba yayin da Declan Gallagher ya jefa kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya ci gaba da kwanciyar hankali don zaɓar Menga don kammala mai sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu yayin da ya sauya Coulibaly da Ryan Kent kuma sauyawar ta kusan samar da tasiri nan take yayin da mai tsaron baya ya shiga Morelos amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya yi tsere daga layinsa zuwa toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi don yin wasa daidai da irin wasan da suke jin dadin, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna shafe dogon ball bayan dogon ball.
Holt zai iya samun nasara a karshe amma McGregor ya tashi tsaye don ya musanta Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya kai ga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake neman fanareti a baya yayin da ya yi rikici da Jacobs amma kuma Thomson ya juya.
