Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya kai hari kan namiji mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da yake takawa a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na Game of Thrones.
Amma jarumin mai shekara 31 ya yi watsi da ra'ayin jarumi mai tsattsauran ra'ayi, yana cewa irin wannan rawar a kan allon yana nufin cewa yara maza suna jin kamar dole ne su kasance masu wuya don a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa 'wani abu ya tafi ba daidai ba' kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar cutar namiji a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri abokin aikinsa na Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, kuma mai shekaru 31, ya yarda yana jin 'da gaske' game da magance batun.
'Ina jin kaina, sosai, a wannan lokacin - ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji? 'in ji shi.
'Menene muka koya wa maza sa'ad da suke girma, game da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ta yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na alhakin karuwar namiji mai guba godiya ga halayen maza.
Ya ci gaba: 'Menene aka haifa kuma menene aka koya?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma kan tituna, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance da wannan yanayin kasancewa namiji?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a zamaninmu - ta yaya za mu canza hakan?
Domin babu shakka akwai abin da bai dace ba da samari suke yi.'
A cikin hirar ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones ba ko kuma a lokacin da jerin ya ƙare a lokacin rani na gaba, yana cewa ya 'yi tare da fagen fama da dawakai'.
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit za ta fito a cikin sake farfado da Sam Shepard na Gaskiya West wanda shine labarin mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ɗan fashi ne.
Actor kwanan nan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin haduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya fito daga Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ta wannan hanyar ta ba ni iyalina na gaba, da rayuwata daga nan gaba,' in ji shi.
Rose ta buga Ygritte, ƙaunar ƙaunar Kit Jon Snow, a cikin jerin almara na Emmy.
