Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin bai wa 'yan Birtaniya aikin kwana hudu a mako amma a biya su kwanaki biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da wani tsari mai mahimmanci wanda zai ga 'yan Birtaniya suna aiki kwana hudu a mako - amma ana biyan su biyar.
An bayar da rahoton cewa jam'iyyar na son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu ta hanyar ba su kuɗin da aka samu ta hanyar juyin juya halin ilimin kere kere (AI).
Za a ga ma'aikata suna jin daɗin hutu na kwana uku a ƙarshen mako - amma har yanzu suna karɓar albashi ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai "dace" da ajandar tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin karkatar da kasar a madadin ma'aikata.
An amince da sauyawa zuwa mako na kwana hudu ta Majalisar Kungiyoyin Kungiyoyin Kungiyoyi a matsayin wata hanya ga ma'aikata don cin gajiyar canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da wani nazari kan manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba zai faru cikin dare ba amma aikin kwana hudu a mako burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na sake daidaita tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma tsarin dabarun masana'antu na jam'iyyar".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da za ta amince da irin wannan ra'ayin ba, tare da Jam'iyyar Green Party da ke yin alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a mako a lokacin yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
A halin yanzu jam'iyyar Labour ba ta amince da wannan burin ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Matsayin aiki na kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce ta jam'iyyar kuma jam'iyyar ba ta la'akari da hakan ba".
