Menene Bikin 'Yan Kasar Duniya kuma Shin Ya Yi Wani Abu don Rage Talauci?
A wannan Asabar New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da ke yin aiki da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa; kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, Bikin Baƙi na Duniya zai ga dubun dubatar mutane suna zuwa Babban Lawn na Central Park ba kawai don jin daɗin ayyuka kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin Baƙi na Duniya, wanda aka bayyana a cikin 2012, ci gaba ne na Tsarin Talauci na Duniya, ƙungiyar ba da shawara ta duniya da ke fatan kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar ƙara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaƙi da shi.
Don karɓar tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan kuɗi don tikiti na VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka, ko "ayyuka" kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen ta kasance da shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da kide kide da wake-wake hanya ce ta kwarai ta lallashe mutane su bukaci a dauki mataki, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" - mutane suna jin kamar suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kai ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rikodin "aiki" sama da miliyan 19 daga magoya bayanta, suna turawa zuwa ga wasu manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyuka sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 wanda aka saita don shafar rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 zuwa 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawura 390 da sanarwar da ta samo asali daga ayyukanta, aƙalla dala biliyan 10 daga cikinsu an riga an biya ko an tara kuɗi.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka tabbatar sun yi tasiri kai tsaye kan kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duk duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu aiwatar da manufofin da ke Birtaniya da suka himmatu wajen "taimaka wa yara su bunkasa zuwa cikakkiyar damar su", suna alkawarin samar wa Rwanda da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun karbi tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa, da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin tarihin", jakadan The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman ya fada wa taron yayin wani wasan kwaikwayo a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki ayyuka sama da 5,000 da ke kira ga Burtaniya da ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da tallafin kudi don wani shiri, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai isa ga mata da yara miliyan 5 tare da ayyukan abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga daya daga cikin tambayoyin da ake yi a shafin yanar gizon ta da tambaya "me ya sa kake tunanin za mu iya kawo karshen matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ya amsa: "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin za mu faɗi kuma mu kasa.
Amma, kamar manyan 'yancin jama'a da kuma 'yan adawa da wariyar launin fata a gabanmu, za mu yi nasara, domin mun fi karfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe na cikin wasu daga cikin ayyukan da ke yin aiki a taron na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
