Zinke ya yi zargin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman, inda take aiki a gayyatar gwamnatin da ta halatta - hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Na yi imanin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son yin sulhu kan makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, kudancin kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, a cewar jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin magance shi.
"Amurka tana da wannan damar, tare da Sojojin Ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna bude, kuma, idan ya cancanta, don toshewa, don tabbatar da cewa makamashin su ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke yana jawabi ne ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta wacce ke daukar kanta a matsayin "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya je ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke mu'amala da Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa sun yi daidai.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shine, fiye da ƙasa, amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha a matsayin "fararen fararen hula" tare da tattalin arziki wanda ya dogara da burbushin mai.
Bayanan sun zo ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas ta zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, mafi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don wannan dalili, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, gami da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun mai na "Nord Stream 2" wanda bai dace ba, wanda a cewar Trump, ya sanya Berlin "abokin" Moscow.
Moscow ta maimaita cewa bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 da ya kai dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka karfin bututun da ke yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawa da Washington ga aikin kawai yana haifar da dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na gasa mara kyau.
"Na yi imanin muna da ra'ayin cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki don yin matsin lamba ba kuma masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo mummunan martani daga Jamus, wadda ta sake tabbatar da jajircewarta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Tarayyar Masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta nisanta kanta da manufofin makamashin EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi "Kulawa" A Tsayar da Shugaban Kasa A 2020, Sanatan Massachusetts Ya Ce
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta "duba sosai" a neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar zango.
A yayin taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da gudu.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace kuma hakan ya hada da mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da neman shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci kan Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron gari, yana cewa yana "karɓar wannan gundumar a hanyar da ba daidai ba.
"Ina cikin damuwa har zuwa ƙasusuwana game da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta fito fili ta soki Trump da dan takararsa na Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani tweet a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "ba shakka muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin zabe".
Wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis, duk da haka, ya nuna cewa yawancin masu zaben Warren ba sa ganin ya kamata ta yi takara a shekarar 2020.
Kashi hamsin da takwas na masu jefa kuri'a "mai yiwuwa" na Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata sanatan ya yi takara ba, a cewar binciken Cibiyar Binciken Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk / Boston Globe.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin ɗari sun goyi bayan irin wannan zaɓen.
Binciken ya nuna ƙarin goyon baya ga takarar tsohon Gwamna Deval Patrick, tare da kashi 38 cikin ɗari suna goyon bayan yiwuwar gudu da kashi 48 cikin ɗari a kan hakan.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da aka tattauna dangane da yiwuwar gudanar da zaben 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance a watan Janairu, Associated Press ta ruwaito.
Sarah Palin ta ambaci Track Palin ta PTSD a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin tashin hankali a gida a daren Litinin
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da yake fuskanta yana dawowa, zan iya danganta shi da sauran iyalai waɗanda ke jin tasirin PTSD da wasu raunin da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su", in ji ta ga masu sauraro a wani taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama shi "giwa a cikin dakin" kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji, "sun dawo da ɗan bambanci, sun dawo da wuya, sun dawo suna mamakin ko akwai girmamawa ga abin da 'yan'uwansu sojoji da' yan jirgin sama, da kowane memba na soja, ya ba da ƙasar. "
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an zarge shi da cin zarafin mata a cikin gida, tsoma baki tare da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar makami yayin maye, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun Ma'aikatar 'Yan Sanda ta Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da D.C. sun goyi bayan kalubalen sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia suna goyon bayan kalubalantar doka game da sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana mafaka ga wadanda ke tserewa daga gungun mutane ko tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun gabatar da wata takarda ta abokantaka a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a cikin karar Grace v. Sessions da Kungiyar 'Yancin Bil'adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta game da manufofin tarayya ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta "da 'ya'yansa maza masu aikata muguntar' yan bindiga, " sun ci zarafinta amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi buƙatar mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke samar da adadi mai yawa na masu neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar matsaloli masu yawa tare da ƙungiyoyi da tashin hankali na gida.
Sabuwar manufar mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin 2014 na Hukumar Kula da Fitowar Baƙi wanda ya ba da izinin baƙi marasa izini da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida don neman mafaka.
Babban Lauyan District na Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na jihar, tarayya, da kuma dokokin kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci cewa duk bukatar neman mafaka za a yanke hukunci a kan takamaiman hujjoji da yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan haramcin ya saba wa wannan ka'idar", in ji abokin kotun.
Lauyoyi sun kara da cewa a cikin gajeren cewa manufar hana masu shigowa da shi yana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa kuma "samar da ma'aikata masu mahimmanci".
Babban lauyan Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga cin zarafin gida da tashin hankalin ƙungiyoyi a watan Yuni.
"Ana samun mafaka ga wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoro saboda launin fata, addini, kasa, ko kasancewa cikin wata kungiya ta zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar da ya yi a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka ta sauƙaƙa duk matsalolin ba - har ma da matsaloli masu tsanani - waɗanda mutane ke fuskanta kowace rana a duk faɗin duniya.
