"Ina jin damuwa sosai", in ji Risa Kusuma, wata uwa 'yar shekara 35, tana ta'azantar da ɗanta da ke fama da zazzabi a wani wurin da ake ceto mutane a birnin Palu da aka halaka.
"Kowane minti motar asibiti tana kawo gawarwaki.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da ƙarancin yawa".
An ga mazauna sun koma gidajen da aka lalata, suna tattara kayan da ke cikin ruwa, suna ƙoƙarin ceton duk abin da za su iya samu.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni kuma asibitoci, da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta lalata, sun cika.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dwi Haris, wanda ya ji rauni a baya da kafada, sun huta a waje da Asibitin Sojojin Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda ci gaba da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi.
Ya yi kuka sa'ad da ya gaya mana yadda girgizar ƙasar ta girgiza ɗakin da yake zama a ciki da matarsa da 'yarsa.
"Ba mu da lokacin ceton kanmu.
Na kasance a cikin kango, ina tsammanin, "in ji Haris ga Associated Press, yana mai cewa danginsa suna cikin gari don bikin aure.
"Na ji matata tana kuka don taimako, amma sai ta yi shiru.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita da ɗana ba.
Ina fata suna lafiya".
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da 'cin zarafi' da 'tallace-tallacen farfaganda'
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani shafi hudu a cikin wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba da ta gabata ya ambaci karin kudin da aka biya na jaridar China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi yawan sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin Trump cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa Reuters cewa sabon mataki ne a wani kamfen da Washington ke karawa don matsa lamba kan China.
Duk da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci wanda ya sa suka sanya haraji kan shigo da kayayyaki.
Kudaden da kasar Sin ta saka a farkon yakin cinikayya an tsara su ne don kai hari ga masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa wadanda ke goyon bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, masana kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa na dogon lokaci, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Branstad ya rubuta a wani labarin ra'ayi a jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, cewa China "yana ƙara wannan zalunci ta wajen buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a jaridarmu ta 'yanci".
"A yada farfaganda, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin magana da' yancin 'yan jarida ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a kantin jaridu a kan titi a nan Beijing, za ku sami muryoyin da ba su yarda ba kuma ba za ku ga wani hakikanin tunani game da ra'ayoyin da mutanen China za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin yatsan hannu na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta kasar Sin, "in ji shi.
Ya daɗa cewa "ɗaya daga cikin jaridu mafiya shahara a ƙasar Sin ta ƙi buga" labarinsa, ko da yake bai faɗi jaridar ba.
'Yan Republican Sun Kashe Mata Masu Zabe Kafin Zabe Na Tsakiyar Shekara Tare Da Kavanaugh Debacle, Masu Sharhi Sun Yi Gargadi
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican da yawa ke tsaye suna kare dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh a gaban zarge-zarge da yawa na cin zarafin jima'i, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su ga mummunan sakamako, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaɓen tsakiyar zangon da ke tafe.
Motsin zuciyar da ke kewaye da wannan ya kasance mai girma, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Ba za a iya dawo da waɗannan abubuwan ba", Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse ya fada wa The Hill don labarin da aka buga ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) na minti na karshe don neman binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi gobe ba kuma ba a watan Nuwamba ba", Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn ta ce a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun rera waka "Nuwamba na zuwa!" yayin da suke zanga-zanga a cikin zauren Majalisar Dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da Kwamitin Shari'a suka zaɓi ci gaba da zaɓen Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dokta Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ta ruwaito.
"Jami'ar dimokiradiyya da kuma motsawa za su kasance a kan taswirar", Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin siyasa ba tare da jam'iyya ba, ya gaya wa shafin yanar gizon.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi yawa; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin unguwannin karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban kasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a".
Tun kafin shaidar Ford ta bayyana dalla-dalla game da zargin ta na cin zarafin mata da aka zaba a Kotun Koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya fuskantar mummunan sakamako idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da tabbatarwa.
"Wannan ya zama rikici ga GOP", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba batun kuri'ar kwamitin bane ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko kuma an sanya Kavanaugh a kan benci, har ma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka magance wannan da yadda suka bi da ita", Guy Cecil, darektan Fifikowa Amurka, kungiyar da ke taimakawa wajen zabar 'yan Democrat, ya nuna wa tashar labarai.
Koyaya, Amurkawa suna da ɗan rarrabuwa game da wanda za su yi imani da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da ɗan ƙara kasancewa tare da na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da kari, kashi 38 cikin dari sun ce suna tunanin Kavanaugh mai yiwuwa ko kuma tabbas ya yi ƙarya a lokacin shaidarsa, yayin da kashi 30 cikin dari kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
Bayan turawa daga Flake, FBI a halin yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya gabatar da akalla wani mai zargin, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ta ruwaito.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a karkashin rantsuwa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya bugu ya yi mata hari yana da shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi zargin cewa dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa yayin da suke halartar wata liyafa a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda Ya Ƙirƙiri Duniyar Yanar Gizo Ya Yi Shirin Ƙirƙirar Sabuwar Intanet da Za Ta Yi Gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, yana kaddamar da wani shiri da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya gina daga dandamali na tushen budewa na Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma abin da mutane ke da izinin samun damar shiga wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi dariya cewa niyyar da ke bayan Inrupt shine "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "shafin yanar gizon sirri" ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike guda kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban mamaki game da kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa yana da cikakken zuwa ga mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar irin bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, tsari da ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa sanya Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka ma'aikata da aka ƙulla su yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya na iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken canji inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su gaba daya ya rushe cikin dare.
"Ba mu tambayar su izinin".
A cikin wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "manufa ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka gina akan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da lokacin da yake ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da Daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa sosai game da wannan zamani na gaba na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: WW1 Victoria Cross limamin da aka yi bikin
An yi bikin cika shekaru 100 a garinsu, a kan limamin cocin Ingila da ya lashe lambar yabo ta Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya.
Laftanar Colonel Reverend Bernard Vann ya lashe lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a harin da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an kashe shi da wani maharbi kwanaki hudu daga baya kuma bai san cewa ya lashe lambar yabo ta soja ta Birtaniya ba.
Jikansa biyu sun bayyana wani dutse na tunawa a wani fareti a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce "abin alama ne mai ban mamaki" cewa za a bayyana dutsen daidai shekaru 100 daga nasarar da kakansa ya samu.
A cewar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 Lt Col Vann ya jagoranci bataliyarsa a fadin Canal de Saint-Quentin "ta hanyar hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai tsanani daga filin da bindigogi".
Daga bisani ya yi gaggawa zuwa layin wuta kuma tare da "babban ƙarfin hali" ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya yi amfani da bindiga da hannu ɗaya kuma ya kashe uku daga cikin 'yan tawagar.
An kashe Lt. Col. Vann ne daga wani dan jarida na Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba 1918 - kawai fiye da wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa "wani abu ne da na san ba zan taɓa iya rayuwa ba amma wani abu ne mai tawali'u".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr James Vann sun kuma shimfiɗa wani kayan ado bayan bikin, wanda ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce yana "jin girmamawa sosai da ya taka rawa a cikin faretin" kuma ya kara da cewa "jarumtar gwarzo na gaske ana nuna ta ne ta hanyar goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su bayar".
MMA magoya zauna up dukan dare to watch Bellator 206, suka samu Peppa Pig maimakon
