Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji 'ƙananan' game da jima'i
Tom Daley mai yin iyo a gasar Olympics ya ce ya girma yana jin ya fi kowa daraja domin jima'i - amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Matashin mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni" ba sai da ya je makarantar sakandare.
Da yake magana a farkon Radio 4 Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da haƙƙin gay don ba wa wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce zama iyaye ya sa bai damu da lashe gasar Olympics ba.
Mai gabatar da shirin na dogon lokaci, Kirsty Young, ta dauki wasu watanni saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake bayyana a matsayin mai fashin jirgin ruwa a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "kasa da" kowa da kowa yana girma saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba a cikin zamantakewa don son yara maza da 'yan mata".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, waɗannan jin ƙanƙanta da kuma bambancin da nake yi, su ne ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi na ci gaba da yin nasara".
Ya ce yana son ya nuna cewa shi "wani abu ne", don kada ya ɓata wa kowa rai sa'ad da suka gano cewa shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga ƙarin ƙasashe don dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi magana ne saboda yana jin sa'a da ya iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da wata matsala ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Gwarzon gwarzon duniya sau uku ya ce fadawa cikin soyayya da wani mutum - mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013 - "ya ba ni mamaki".
Daley ya auri mai lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya fi shi shekaru 20, a bara amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka fuskanci abubuwa da yawa a wannan ƙaramin shekarunka" - ya halarci gasar Olympics na farko yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu sanadiyyar ciwon daji bayan shekara uku - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekarunsa da ya fuskanci irin wannan yanayi mai kyau da kuma na baƙin ciki.
Ma'auratan sun zama iyaye a watan Yuni, ga ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "duk hangen nesan" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da ya shafi 'Ina bukatar lashe lambar zinare,'" in ji shi.
"Ka san abin da, akwai abubuwa mafi girma fiye da zinare na Olympics.
Kyautar zinariyar Olympics ita ce Robbie".
Ɗansa yana da suna kamar mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da ciwon daji a kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan karshe da ya tambaya shi ne ko suna da tikiti na London 2012 - kamar yadda yake so ya kasance a jere na gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba 'ba za ka kasance a kusa da zama a kan mahaifin farko ba,'" in ji shi.
"Ina rike da hannunsa yayin da ya daina numfashi kuma ba sai da ya daina numfashi ba kuma ya mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba shi da nasara", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkinsa a dukan rayuwata - in yi iyo a gaban jama'ar gida a wasannin Olympics, babu abin da ya fi wannan", in ji shi.
Hakanan ya ba da waƙar farko da ya zaɓa - Proud by Heather Small - wanda ya yi masa magana a cikin ginin zuwa gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu ya ba shi goosebumps.
Desert Island Discs yana kan BBC Radio 4 ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 BST.
Mickelson da ba shi da kyau a gasar Ryder Cup ranar Asabar
Ba'amurke Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi lokacin da ya buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma dole ne ya juya yanayin sa don kauce wa zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ke buga wasan a karo na 12 a gasar, ya yi wa kyaftin Jim Furyk kwallo a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar aikin, kamar yadda sau da yawa ya kasance ga Amurka, babban mai nasara sau biyar ya raba ranarsa tsakanin kasancewa mai tayar da hankali da kuma aiki a kan wasansa a kan iyakar da fatan gyara abin da ke damunsa.
Ba mai tsananin kai tsaye ba a cikin direbobi har ma a saman aikinsa, dan shekara 48 bai dace da yanayin Le Golf National ba, inda dogon tsauraran matakai ke azabtar da harbi mara kyau.
Kuma idan hanya kadai ba ta isa ba, Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya fuskanci zakaran Birtaniya na Francesco Molinari, wanda ya hada kai da rookie Tommy Fleetwood don lashe dukkan wasanninsu hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, da suka yi kasa da maki hudu a fara wasannin guda 12, suka fara da zafi, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa yana da tabbaci a kan mutanensa, amma ba zai iya faɗa wani abu ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci rawar da yake da ita a yau, ya bugo baya ya rungume ni ya ce zai shirya gobe.
"Yana da gaba gaɗi sosai a kansa.
Shi dan wasan Hall of Fame ne kuma ya karawa kungiyoyin da yawa a baya, kuma a wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin fiye da haka, amma haka ya kasance kuma wannan ita ce hanyar da muka yi tunanin dole ne mu tafi.
Yana son ya fita waje, kamar kowa".
Mickelson zai wuce rikodin Nick Faldo na mafi yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Hakan na iya nuna karshen aikinsa na gasar Ryder Cup wanda bai taba kaiwa matsayin da ya kafa ba.
Mickelson ya samu nasara 18, shan kashi 20 da kuma rabin wasa bakwai, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ta kawo wasu abubuwa marasa amfani ga tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ba'a, mai hankali, yana son yin dariya da mutane, kuma babban mutum ne don samun shi a cikin ɗakin ƙungiyar", in ji shi.
"Ina ganin 'yan wasan matasa sun yi farin ciki da yin wasa da shi, wannan makon, wanda ya kasance mai ban sha'awa don ganin.
Yana ba da abubuwa da yawa fiye da wasa kawai".
Kyaftin din Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa babban jagora zai iya ɓace nan ba da jimawa ba
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai, ya san daga kwarewa cewa babban jagoranci zuwa ranar karshe a gasar cin kofin Ryder zai iya zama da sauƙi ya zama tafiya mara kyau.
Dan Dan Dan ya fara wasa a wasan 1997 a Valderrama, inda ƙungiyar da Seve Ballesteros ke jagoranta ta sami ci gaba da maki biyar akan Amurkawa amma kawai ta wuce layin gamawa tare da hanci a gaba ta hanyar mafi ƙanƙanta, ta lashe 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna ci gaba da tunatar da kanku cewa muna da babban jagoranci a Valderrama; muna da babban jagoranci a Brookline, inda muka yi asara, da kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma kawai, "in ji Bjorn, wanda aka nuna a hoto, bayan kallon ajin 2018 ya ci 5-3 duka a ranar Juma'a da jiya don ya jagoranci 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Don haka tarihi zai nuna min da kowa a wannan tawagar cewa wannan ba ta ƙare ba.
Za ka yi cikakken bore gobe.
Ka fita can ka yi dukan abin da ya dace.
Wannan ba ya ƙare har sai kun sami maki a kan allon.
Muna da wata manufa, kuma ita ce mu yi kokarin lashe wannan kofin, kuma a nan ne muke mai da hankali.
Na ce tun farko, ina mai da hankali kan 'yan wasa 12 da ke gefenmu, amma mun san abin da ke tsaye a gefe guda - manyan' yan wasa a duniya. "
Da yake yana farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi a filin golf mai wuya, Bjorn ya daɗa: "Ba zan taɓa yin hakan da sauri ba.
Gobe wata dabba ce dabam.
Gobe ne za a gabatar da wasu ayyuka, kuma wannan wani abu ne daban da za a yi.
Yana da kyau ka kasance a waje da abokin tarayya idan abubuwa suna tafiya da kyau, amma idan kana waje da kanka, to, an gwada ka da cikakken ƙarfinka a matsayin mai wasan golf.
Wannan shi ne sakon da ya kamata ka isar wa 'yan wasan, shi ne ka samu mafi kyau daga kanka gobe.
Yanzu, ka bar abokin aikinka a baya kuma dole ne ya tafi ya sami mafi kyau daga kansa, ma. "
Sabanin Bjorn, abokin karawar Jim Furyk zai nemi 'yan wasansa su yi aiki mafi kyau a matsayin mutum fiye da yadda suka yi a matsayin abokan tarayya, banda Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka tara maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk da kansa ya kasance a bangarorin biyu na waɗannan manyan juyin juya halin na kwanakin ƙarshe, kasancewar yana cikin ƙungiyar masu nasara a Brookline kafin ya ƙare a matsayin mai rasa yayin da Turai ta cire "Miracle a Medina".
"Na tuna da kowace kalma", in ji shi a lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin din a 1999, ya tara 'yan wasansa a ranar karshe.
"Muna da muhimman wasanni 12 gobe, amma kuna so ku fara da sauri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brookline, kamar yadda kuka gani a Madinah.
Lokacin da wannan motsi ya tafi hanya ɗaya, yana sanya matsin lamba sosai a kan waɗannan wasannin tsakiya.
Mun kafa jerinmu daidai da haka kuma mun sanya mutane a cikin salon da muke jin kamar, ka sani, muna ƙoƙarin yin sihiri gobe. "
An ba Thomas aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar gwagwarmaya kuma yana fuskantar Rory McIlroy a cikin babban wasan, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter sauran Turawa a saman rabin tsari.
"Na yi amfani da wannan rukuni na mutane a cikin wannan tsari domin ina tsammanin yana rufe duk hanyar ta hanyar", in ji Bjorn na zaɓin da ya yi na masu aure.
An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
Ya kamata a fara amfani da sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai kasance a can ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da tsadar dusar ƙanƙara, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An dage aikin "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwan sabbin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton mai magana da yawun soja.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga cikin Sojojin Ruwa a cikin 2014, amma matsalolin bayan bayarwa sun shafi makomar wannan babban aikin.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar sojin ruwa ta umarce su a shekarar 2007 za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An fahimci cewa za su sami bindiga mai ƙarfi, jerin makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoyewa, kamar rage radar, infrared da sa hannu na sauti.
Sauran muhimman abubuwa sun hada da tsawon lokacin kiyayewa - ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa har tsawon shekaru biyu daga tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma, jinkirin da ake yi a kai a kai yana nufin cewa jiragen yaƙi na zamani - da ake cewa suna ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje - za su riga su zama tsofaffi kafin su soma aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
Frigate mai suna F125 ya zama sanannen sanarwa a bara, lokacin da Sojojin Ruwa na Jamus suka ƙi karɓar jirgin ruwa kuma suka mayar da shi zuwa Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgi zuwa mai gina jirgi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san komai game da dalilan da ke bayan dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu mahimman "kasawa na software da kayan aiki" waɗanda suka sa jirgin yaƙin ya zama mara amfani idan an tura shi cikin aikin yaƙi.
Rashin software ya kasance da mahimmanci kamar yadda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na kimanin 120 - kawai rabin ma'aikata a kan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Har ila yau, ya bayyana cewa jirgin yana da nauyin kima wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Navy don ƙara haɓaka a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa "Rheinland-Pfalz" mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da kayan aiki da ba su da kyau, farashin aikin - har da horar da ma'aikatan - ma yana zama matsala.
An ce ya kai biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6) - daga biliyan 2.2 na farko.
Matsalolin da ke damun sabbin jiragen ruwa sun zama masu mahimmanci musamman a cikin hasken gargadi na kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin sojojin ruwa na Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa a zahiri Sojan Ruwa suna "gazawa da jiragen ruwa masu iya aiki".
Jami'in ya ce batun ya kara yawaitarwa a tsawon lokaci, saboda an cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da wasu jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi baƙin ciki cewa babu ɗayan jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da suka iya shiga cikin Navy.
Hukumar Kula da Ƙasar ta saurari labaran da ake yi a ɓoye na waɗannan ƙwari
Wani sabon bincike da ake yi a wani fili a ƙasar Scotland yana nufin sanin yadda waɗannan ƙudaje suke amfani da wurin don neman abinci.
Ana sa ran cewa binciken zai ba da ƙarin haske game da halayen waɗannan dabbobi masu tashi da ba a taɓa gani ba kuma zai taimaka wajen tsara yadda za a kiyaye su a nan gaba.
Binciken da masana kimiyya a National Trust for Scotland za su yi zai biye wa pipistrelles na yau da kullum da soprano da kuma launin ruwan kasa da kuma Daubenton bats a Inverewe Gardens a Wester Ross.
Za a sanya na'urori na musamman a wurare masu mahimmanci a kusa da dukiyar don lura da ayyukan bat a duk tsawon kakar.
Ma'aikatan NHS da masu sa kai za su kuma gudanar da binciken wayar hannu ta amfani da na'urorin gano abubuwa.
Binciken ƙwararru na sauti na duk rikodin zai tabbatar da yawan kiran ƙwari da kuma nau'in da ke yin abin da.
Za a samar da taswirar mazauni da rahoto don samar da cikakken hoto game da halayensu.
Rob Dewar, mai ba da shawara a kan kiyaye yanayi a NTS, yana fatan cewa sakamakon zai nuna wuraren da suke da muhimmanci ga waɗannan ƙudaje da kuma yadda kowannensu yake amfani da su.
Wannan bayanin zai taimaka wajen tantance fa'idodin aikin kula da mazaunin kamar ƙirƙirar ciyayi da kuma yadda za a kiyaye gandun daji don barbashi da sauran nau'ikan da ke da alaƙa.
Yawan 'yan kunar bakin wake a Scotland da kuma sauran ƙasashen Birtaniya sun ragu sosai a cikin ƙarni na ƙarshe.
Ana yi musu barazana saboda aikin gine-gine da kuma ci gaba da ke shafan gidaje da kuma rashin wurin zama.
Ƙarƙashin iska da kuma hasken wuta suna iya zama haɗari, kamar yadda takarda da wasu abubuwa da ake amfani da su wajen gina gine-gine suke da haɗari, da kuma hare-haren da wasu da aka fi so suke yi.
Baƙi ba makafi ba ne.
Duk da haka, saboda dabi'un farautar dare kunnuwansu sun fi idanunsu amfani idan ya zo ga kama ganima.
Suna amfani da wata dabara mai ƙwarewa ta gano inda suke don su san inda akwai ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma abubuwan da za su hana su tashi.
