Wani jami'i daga jihar Tennessee ya gaya wa Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee, cewa Abercrombie ya fita daga tiyata a Cibiyar Kiwon Lafiya ta Vanderbilt.
Harris ya kara da cewa "babu cikakken bayani kan nau'in / girman rauni har yanzu" kuma Jihar Tennessee na kokarin gano lokacin da rauni ya faru.
Abercrombie, dan shekara ta biyu ne a shekararsa ta biyu, yana cikin kakar wasa ta farko da ya yi a jihar Tennessee bayan ya koma daga Illinois.
