Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, tare da tsammanin adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da katse sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga gundumar Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke ƙarshen wani kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafa shi.
Donggala yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙasa da lardi, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan jigon tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin gabar teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na Nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya taɓa kai wa Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a garin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, wata guguwar tsunami ta addabi yammacin Donggala kuma ta kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya addabi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi daga cikinsu a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin tsibirin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a kudancin tsibirin, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta auku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, a bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami mai tsayi mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa da ba ta da zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da mutane suka tuna da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa na 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon faduwar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani wuri na ɗan lokaci.
An Kama Babbar 'Yar Sarah Palin Bisa Zargin Tashin hankali A Cikin Gida
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakiyar shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da zargin cin zarafi.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin tashin hankali a cikin gida, tsoma baki tare da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da tsayayya da kamawa, a cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata mace da ta san ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran' yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin aikata laifuka, ya ɗauki wayarta daga gare ta.
Ana tsare da Palin a gidan yarin Mat-Su da aka tsare a kan $500 bond ba tare da garanti ba, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana kansa "ba shi da laifi, tabbas" lokacin da aka tambaye shi ya nemi laifinsa, in ji gidan rediyon.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin zai iya zama kurkuku har zuwa shekara guda da kuma tara $ 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin Class B, wanda za a iya hukunta shi da ranar kurkuku da kuma tarar $ 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karon farko da aka shigar da tuhumar aikata laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin da ake yi.
A halin yanzu ana shari'ar ne a gaban kotun tsoffin sojoji ta Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 an tuhume shi da cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki a rahoton wani laifin tashin hankali na gida, da kuma mallakar makami yayin buguwa dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta yi zargin cewa ya buge ta a fuska.
Kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin a shekarar 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da PTSD da ya samo asali daga aikinsa a Iraki.
