Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yi ba a jihar don aikata laifi tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, an yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, yana yanka masu tafiya da masu hawan keke a hanyarsa a ranar Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov "da gangan" ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a gundumar Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin wadannan zarge-zargen suna da hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban juri'in tarayya ya yi wa Saipov hukuncin kisa 22 wanda ya hada da tuhume-tuhume takwas na kisan kai don taimakawa cin hanci da rashawa, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhume-tuhume na tashin hankali da lalata motocin hawa.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka tsara da kuma yin la'akari", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a matsayin "abin ƙyama, mugunta da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lahani, da asara ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", sanarwar niyyar ta ce.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka fara shari'ar hukuncin kisa a gundumar New York.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa na kashe masu samar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka zartar da hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya ta New York shine a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisan kai don yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin dadi game da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu wahayi don kai harin bayan kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar karar.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya yi ikirarin rashin laifi a kan tuhumar da ake masa da laifin aikata laifuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a bayyane yake sun yi takaici" da hukuncin da ake tuhuma.
"Muna ganin shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifin da ake yi na ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai tsawaita cutar da wadannan abubuwan suka haifar ga duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisa na Tory sun ce ya kamata a sanya Nigel Farage a matsayin wanda zai jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin 'tara sojojin jama'a' a yau yayin zanga-zangar a taron 'yan Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa dole ne su 'ji zafi' daga masu shakkar Turai - kamar yadda wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya nuna cewa ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawa da EU.
Dan majalisa mai kare dangi Peter Bone ya fadawa masu zanga-zangar a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta fita" a yanzu idan Mr Farage ne Sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sasantawa tsakanin bangarorin da suka rabu ya kara bayyanawa da 'yan Tories masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a kasar da suka shiga zanga-zangar daban da ke adawa da Brexit a birnin.
Firayim Minista na gwagwarmayar ci gaba da shirin sulhunta na Chequers a cikin hanyar da ta dace a yayin da ake kai hare-hare daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu ci gaba da kasancewa da EU.
Allies sun dage cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da mummunan martani - kuma tilasta masu shakkar Turai da ma'aikatan aiki su zabi tsakanin kunshin ta da 'hargitsi'.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa taron 'Leave Means Leave' a Solihull cewa yana son 'barin 'Chequers'.
Ya ce ya kamata a sanya Farage a matsayin mai kula da harkokin kasuwanci da kuma kula da tattaunawar da za a yi da Brussels.
Ya ce: 'Da a ce shi ne yake shugabanci, da mun riga mun fita yanzu.
'Yan majalisar Wellingborough sun kara da cewa: 'Zan tsaya ga Brexit amma muna bukatar mu watsar da Chequers.'
Da yake bayyana adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama masu biyayya ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayin da ake cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya sauya tun bayan zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son ci gaba ba gaskiya bane".
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma yana wajen gangamin, yana gaya wa manema labarai: 'Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista, saurari mutane.
'Cakulan ba shi da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su zabe shi ba, ba shi da kyau a jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu waɗanda ke yin zanga-zanga a kan tituna kuma suna zaɓe mu a farkon wuri.
Ka bar wasan da kake yi kuma ka soma saurarawa.'
A cikin wata sanarwa da ta aika wa Mrs May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci suna rike da ayyukansu idan sun cika alkawuransu".
Mista Farage ya ce dole ne a sa 'yan siyasa su 'ji zafi' idan suna gab da cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
'Yanzu batun amana ne tsakanin mu - mutane - da kuma siyasarmu,' in ji shi.
'Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu 'ba za mu bari ku fita da yin hakan ba'
A wani sako da ya aike wa taron masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke gab da cin amanar Brexit, su ji zafi.
'Muna tattara sojojin mutanen wannan kasa da suka bamu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za su huta ba har sai mun zama 'yanci, masu cin gashin kansu, masu alfahari da Burtaniya.'
A halin yanzu, masu ci gaba da tafiya a Birmingham kafin gudanar da taron na sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi ta yin amfani da tutar Tories da ke adawa da Brexit bayan kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Shugaban jam'iyyar Labour Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservative ba'a kan matsalolin tsaro da suka sha wahala tare da aikace-aikacen jam'iyyar yayin da taron ya buɗe.
"Waɗannan mutane ne waɗanda ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da duk fasahar don Kanada da ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da ƙwanƙwasawa, don cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
'Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu irin wannan abu kamar mai kyau Brexit, 'ya kara da cewa.
Warren na shirin duba yadda zai yi takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi "duba-da-kai wajen neman shugaban kasa" bayan zaben Nuwamba.
Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan jam'iyyar Democrat ta Massachusetts ya yi magana game da makomar ta a yayin taron gari a yammacin Massachusetts ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai yawan sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, yana neman sake zaben a watan Nuwamba da wakilin jihar GOP Geoff Diehl, wanda ya kasance shugaban yakin neman zaben Trump na 2016 na Massachusetts.
