Yadda yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing
Farkon tashin hankalin yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya yi kururuwa, kuma yayin da yakin ya yi nisa da ƙarshe, wani rabuwa tsakanin ƙasashen na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, masana sun ce.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, ya yi gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya faru a wannan makon tare da sabbin haraji da ke shafar abubuwa masu darajar dala biliyan 200 (£ 150 biliyan), wanda ke yin haraji da kusan rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta yi martani a kowane lokaci ta hanyar irin wannan, kwanan nan ta ɗora haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari kan kayayyakin Amurka na dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin yin daidai da Amurka, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu mafi girma ba zai iya yin aiki ba nan ba da jimawa ba.
Samun Washington ta ja da baya yana nufin mika wuya ga bukatun, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta iya yin wasanninta daidai, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya na Amurka na iya tallafawa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da ke nazarin Asiya a wata ƙungiyar bincike mai suna Center for New American Security ta ce: "Gaskiyar cewa za a iya yin saurin yanke shawara a siyasa a Washington ko Beijing zai iya sa tattalin arziki ya yi sanyi a kowace ƙasa ya fi yadda mutane suke tsammani".
Suriya 'a shirye take' don 'yan gudun hijira su dawo, in ji Ministan Harkokin Waje
Syria ta ce a shirye take da dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ya lalace sakamakon yakin da ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
Da yake jawabi a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na ingantawa.
Ya ce, "A yau yanayin da ake ciki ya fi karko da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu wajen yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'amuran yau da kullun.
Yanzu duk yanayin ya kasance domin 'yan gudun hijira su koma kasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe daya da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria sama da miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai yarda da taimako ko taimako daga kasashen da ke tallafawa tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Teamungiyar Turai ta ci gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta doke Team USA da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a wajen Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu haka Amurka ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a nahiyar Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ba a Turai tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar yayin da tawagar da ta jagoranci Thomas Bjorn ta Denmark ta kai maki 14.5 da suke bukata don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi fama da mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa harbinsa a cikin ruwa a rami na 16, yana barin wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya haskaka a duk zagayensa, ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka taba zuwa 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya fadi 5&4 daga dan wasan da ya fi kasa a tawagar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowacce ta duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga wasan karshe na Ryder Cup.
Wani tsohon soja na gasar Ryder Cup guda takwas, dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan Turai mafi nasara a gasar duk lokacin da ya samu maki 25.5.
