Sabuntawa na Red Tide: Matsakaicin ya ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka samu daga Hukumar Kifi da Dajin Florida ya nuna raguwar yawan ruwan Red Tide a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana samun rahoton yanayin fure-fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma gundumar Collier - wanda ke nuna raguwar maida hankali.
A flower the Red Tide yana da nisan kilomita 130 na bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin jihohin Lee.
Ana iya samun wasu wurare a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare kaɗan da suka fi na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a cikin County Pasco.
An ba da rahoton matsakaitan maida hankali a cikin ko a bakin tekun Pinellas County a cikin makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan maida hankali a bakin tekun Hillsborough County, baya ga manyan maida hankali a cikin Manatee County, baya ga manyan maida hankali a cikin ko a bakin tekun Sarasota County, baya ga matsakaitan maida hankali a cikin Charlotte County, baya ga manyan maida hankali a cikin ko a bakin tekun Lee County, da ƙananan maida hankali a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da bayar da rahoton ciwon numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma gundumar Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton ciwon numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
